description:
Danny welcomes Annabelle DeSisto (host of Adderall and Compliments) back to the show for a very special/ridiculous/insane POP Dive. They sip wine and do their version of the Kathie Lee & Hoda hour of the TODAY Show. Consider this episode the 5th hour of TODAY. They run through their versions of popular KLG & Hoda segments like "iHoda" and "Wednesday Whaaaattt?"
